transcripts.text: In Vietnam, Robert Mueller rescued fallen Marines under enemy fire.  As a prosecutor and head of the FBI under George W. Bush, Mueller spent decades going after corruption and terrorism.  Republicans trusted Mueller to lead the investigation of Russian interference in the 2016 election.
I have a lot of confidence in Bob Mueller.  I trust him to be honest and fair.  Bob is a straight shooter and should be dealt with as such.
On July 24th, hear him testify about his report before Congress, paid for by Republicans for the rule of law.
